name: Generational Cures
description:
But the Women had heard.
They had known beyond all knowing that the journey to the next was upon them.

They looked down on each aspect of their lineage with patience, love and acceptance.

"We just wanted your to ask for assistance".

This was their message.

It flowed through every breath and wave.

Come forth and ask for their support.

The future of each incarnation after these rested on the knowing of their existence.
